txt.en: War-Tyrant Akúlhun waits your return to Gramsfoot where he will see you rewarded for your service to Lugazag!
You have been recognized as a servant to the master of Lugazag!
'Another servant to Angmar! You are recognized this day with a reward long due. Use it well, maggot!'
Your service to the master of Lugazag is rewarded!
Complete quests for the benefit of Lugazag!
You have performed many services for the master of Lugazag.
